  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>More services and facilities include: 2 championship air-conditioned squash courts, a floodlit tennis court, gymnasium, a rooftop swimming pool and an aerobics studio.The hotel ownes and operates the largest traditional Dhow which sails daily for lunch and dinner. This hotels comes highly recommended and offers a great base to explore Dubai. 
(SC 08/07)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is situated in the heart of Dubai, close to all the major shopping centres and the World Trade Centre. Across the street is the "Creek" River that divides Dubai in Bur Dubai and Deira. It's only 5 minutes from Dubai International Airport and within the business district. The major souks are within walking distance. A fantastic location.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>The luxurious large rooms all enjoy panoramic views of Dubai's Creek. All are furnished in contemporary style in a variety of pastel colours with extra seating available in all the rooms. The marble bathrooms are in excellent condition, as are the bedrooms. All rooms have balconies.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>This is a very large, modern, sandstone-coloured, multi storey building with a large car park at the front.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel offers a variety of cuisine such as Persian, Far Eastern, Japanese and Italian. The cafe serves an excellent buffet as well as snacks during the day. The restaurants are famous in Dubai for serving outstanding cuisine and have won numerous awards. The choice of cuilnary outlets is vast!!</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The medium sized lobby is very well decorated in classic style with elegant seating.</Text>
  </Description>
